graph LR
    NemoGuardrails["NeMo Guardrails<br/>(FastAPI Service)"]

    %% Core Framework Dependencies (Required)
    NemoGuardrails -->|API framework| FastAPI["FastAPI >=0.103.0"]
    NemoGuardrails -->|ASGI server| Uvicorn["Uvicorn >=0.23"]
    NemoGuardrails -->|LLM abstraction| LangChain["LangChain >=0.2.14"]
    NemoGuardrails -->|language parser| Lark["Lark >=1.1.7"]
    NemoGuardrails -->|ANN index| Annoy["Annoy >=1.17.3"]
    NemoGuardrails -->|local embeddings| FastEmbed["FastEmbed >=0.2.2"]
    NemoGuardrails -->|ML inference| ONNX["ONNX Runtime >=1.17.0"]

    %% External LLM Providers (Egress)
    NemoGuardrails -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token"| OpenAI["OpenAI API"]
    NemoGuardrails -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token"| NIM["NVIDIA NIM"]
    NemoGuardrails -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>x-api-key"| Anthropic["Anthropic API"]
    NemoGuardrails -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>api-key"| Azure["Azure OpenAI"]
    NemoGuardrails -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token"| Cohere["Cohere API"]
    NemoGuardrails -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>GCP creds"| VertexAI["Google Vertex AI"]

    %% Optional Infrastructure
    NemoGuardrails -.->|"6379/TCP<br/>thread persistence"| Redis["Redis<br/>(optional)"]
    NemoGuardrails -.->|"4317/TCP gRPC<br/>trace export"| OTel["OpenTelemetry<br/>Collector (optional)"]

    %% In-Process Libraries (Optional)
    NemoGuardrails -.->|PII detection| Presidio["Presidio<br/>(optional)"]
    NemoGuardrails -.->|NLP/NER| SpaCy["spaCy<br/>(en_core_web_lg)"]
    NemoGuardrails -.->|jailbreak patterns| YARA["YARA-Python<br/>(optional)"]

    %% Platform Integration
    RHOAIPlatform["RHOAI Platform<br/>(rhods-operator)"] -->|provisions ingress| NemoGuardrails
    RHOAIPlatform -->|auth enforcement| NemoGuardrails

    %% Build-Time Only
    NemoGuardrails -.->|"build-time model download"| HuggingFace["HuggingFace Hub"]

